title: "What it's like to audit your own systems after watching three platforms get breached"
description: >-
  In 2026, three platforms we use or build like got breached. Here's what
  reading the postmortems made us do — and what we learned about our own
  attack surface as a small shop.
publishedDate: '2026-04-25'
